    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors were not assessed and are flagged as epistemic gaps. The aggregate credibility evidence is insufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class III VAD indication. The assessment is accepted as complete documentation of the credibility gap.",
